{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197883, "create_time": 1654764759, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "显然，他反对以公权力介入审查的方式对抗虚假信息", "timestamp": 1654764759}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197890, "create_time": 1654764824, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 那你想怎么对抗虚假信息", "timestamp": 1654764824}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197894, "create_time": 1654764843, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 你看看文章里面怎么说的呗", "timestamp": 1654764843}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197899, "create_time": 1654764906, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 这个显然是拍脑袋敲出来的？", "timestamp": 1654764906}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197903, "create_time": 1654764949, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "#卡大佐", "timestamp": 1654764949}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197904, "create_time": 1654764964, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "事实上，历史和现实反复证明，不受制约的公权力往往是虚假信息的主要来源之一", "timestamp": 1654764964}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197905, "create_time": 1654764965, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 但今天，我担心的是另一个问题——不是审查制度，而是那些过度地滥用自由表达而产生的大量严重误导的言论，这些言论威胁着我们道德、伦理、公正、明智和理智的世界。我担心滥用言论自由的现象越来越普遍。", "timestamp": 1654764965}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197906, "create_time": 1654764999, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 你要是没有基本的阅读能力，建议回义务教育回炉重造一下。另外:\n#卡大佐", "timestamp": 1654764999}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197909, "create_time": 1654765015, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: #标记弟", "timestamp": 1654765015}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197915, "create_time": 1654765080, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 一是不要让言论自由阻止对虚假信息的谴责并尽我们所能阻止它。", "timestamp": 1654765080}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197916, "create_time": 1654765096, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "让我们回到我们正在面临的问题以及这些威胁的严重性。这不仅只是特定谎言的传播，蓄意的虚假信息和宣传煽动正在严重削弱深厚学问和专业知识本身的理念。虚假信息鼓吹起了强烈的民粹主义，这使得专家常常名誉扫地甚至被公然取笑，也让那种自以为然、刚愎自用的傲慢态度愈演愈烈并成为常态。这种态度与大学格格不入，因为我们是社会中保存和推进人类几千年来奋斗和学习成果的主要机构。在过去的几年里，我们的学院一直是虚假宣传滥用的目标。更危险的是，攻击专业人员、知识分子是法西斯主义和专制政权的常用手段。当我们诋毁某项特定知识时，仔细思考就变得更加困难。我们破坏了一个自决社会利用大量已知信息和思想进行决策的基本任务，这些信息和思想是数百年来历经艰难发展出来的，并安全地保存在我们的学术机构、文化机构和职业机构中。", "timestamp": 1654765096}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197928, "create_time": 1654765151, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 一个人拥有绝对的言论自由吗？是否除了官方审查，我们不能采取任何措施来阻止不良言论？我的回答是绝对不应该这样想。", "timestamp": 1654765151}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 197946, "create_time": 1654765278, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 粘这么多到底在表达什么捏", "timestamp": 1654765278}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198098, "create_time": 1654766703, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "滚", "timestamp": 1654766703}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198179, "create_time": 1654767600, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 这就破防了？无能狂怒费拉不堪", "timestamp": 1654767600}], "create_time": 1654764627, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1654767600, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 15, "pid": 61591, "poll": null, "reply": 15, "text": "# 言论自由理应捍卫，虚假信息亟需谴责\n我常常在这样的场合谈论言论自由和因其衍生的学术自由的光辉。但今天，我担心的是另一个问题——不是审查制度，而是那些过度地滥用自由表达而产生的大量严重误导的言论，这些言论威胁着我们道德、伦理、公正、明智和理智的世界。我担心滥用言论自由的现象越来越普遍。\nhttps://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/517079584", "timestamp": 1654764627}}